"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4OL","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":26770,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/26\/makruh-partial-shave-head\/","url_meta":{"origin":18523,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hair: Discouragement to partially shave head, leave rest","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited partial shaving. It was said to Nafi\u2019, \u201cWhat is partial shaving?\u201d Nafi\u2019 said, \u201cIt is to shave part of a boy\u2019s head and leave the rest.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"Shave it all or\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15928,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/masjid-prayer-twenty-seven-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":18523,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jama&#8217;ah: Prayer in mosque is twenty seven times better","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in congregation is better than prayer alone by twenty-seven degrees.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 645, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 650 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Ibn Qudamah said, \"Congregational prayer is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14904,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/suhur-recite-fifty-ayat\/","url_meta":{"origin":18523,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Prolonging pre-fasting meal before Fajr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: We ate the pre-fasting meal\u00a0with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and then we stood for prayer. It was asked, \u201cHow long was it between the two calls to prayer?\u201d Zayd said, \u201cIt was time enough to recite fifty verses from the Quran.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25637,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/19\/fitrah-cleanliness-ten-acts\/","url_meta":{"origin":18523,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fitrah: Ten acts part of natural cleanliness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTen acts are part of natural instinct: trimming the moustache, letting the beard grow, using the toothstick, sniffing water into the nose, clipping the nails, washing the knuckles, removing hair from the underarms, shaving the pubic hair,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[